Debugging
\layout Standard

If you want to debug Umix, configure it with the option 
\series bold 
--enable-debug
\series default 
.
 This will enable debugging information printed to stderr.
 If you want to enable the dummy mixer that has predefined volume levels
 and other settings, pass the 
\series bold 
\emph on 
--
\emph default 
enable-dummy
\series default 
 to configure, and use the command line option 
\series bold 
-r
\series default 
\emph on 
 dummy.
